Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:37.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.19,0:01:40.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,be my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:42.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.55,0:01:56.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, what a kind person you are."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.75,0:01:57.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.78,0:01:59.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And if I said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.86,0:02:03.40,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan didn't accept my rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I told everything to Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:13.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Having your rosary refused isn't the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:18.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Be more confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:20.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But it's painful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:27.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.27,0:02:32.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.41,0:02:36.31,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then, is it alright if I cry a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:14.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:22.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making everyone worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What had happened isn't that big of a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:31.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan rejected Yumi's rosary when she offered it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.61,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.75,0:03:36.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.76,0:03:38.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,watch your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.04,0:03:43.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wasn't saying Rosa Chinensis was lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:45.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:49.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But this is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:53.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's probably not something worth telling others,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,since this makes everyone worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,In addition, there's something I want to request from everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:02.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A request?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:08.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I don't want any of you to become involved with what's going on between Yumi and Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please just watch over Yumi from a distance,{P2C protect - watch over?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:16.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,rather than becoming involved by pitying her or hating Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is their problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll be doing the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Since Sachiko, the older sister, is asking us to do this,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:34.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,we're in no position to interfere. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, you haven't given up yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:57.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:02.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan's been hurt much more than me all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.63,0:05:06.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:16.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A few days later...{}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:31.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A New Year's party at Sachiko-sama's house!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And only girls are allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:39.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Onee-sama, thank you for the invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:41.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You'll come?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:43.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you'll have me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've already received permission from my parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:49.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and I've gotten confirmation from Yoshino-san and Shimako-san through the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:52.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:56.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I invited Touko as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:03.51,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:05.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not giving you a chance to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:12.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,She might not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.67,0:06:13.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then, I thought it was a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.35,0:06:21.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I feel that Touko-chan will just get further and further away if you don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:22.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:26.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:29.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though I told everyone to just watch over you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.82,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I immediately started being meddlesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:36.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Are you an esper? You read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:40.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:44.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I'm your Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And that's all I need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're right. {Maybe a more fitting word. Can't think of one.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.32,0:06:57.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Saeko obaa-sama will be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:18.23,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Obaa-sama is a term used for women of middle-age or older.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:21.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good day to you, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:28.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes, Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.42,0:07:35.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-sama, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:42.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have to apologize to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to apologize and never bring it up again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:49.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is this about Touko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:55.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I've always thought that it would be great if Touko became your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.71,0:08:01.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No, that it would be great if you would be willing to become Touko's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:06.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I thought that you didn't think much of Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:12.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,So that's why I was so sad when you tried to take care of Touko with such simple intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:14.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:20.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You were thinking very seriously about Touko, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:22.54,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.90,0:08:27.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Turning down someone's proposal for sisterhood is neither right nor wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:32.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I definitely don't think that lying to yourself is a good thing either!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:38.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Noriko-chan, you think Touko-chan doesn't hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.37,0:08:40.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:47.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then I must've been the one that made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.85,0:08:49.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:54.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,About the time, the place, or even her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe even the way I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:08.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Did you guys wait long?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:12.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nope. We got here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.88,0:09:15.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:24.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Could this be is your first time being together for the New Year!?{}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.55,0:09:25.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sorry! I didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.62,0:09:30.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll go somewhere else, so please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What are you being so considerate for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:37.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um, what about Rei-sama and Yoshino-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:39.52,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Those two said they would go there directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:42.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Then how about we head over there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.51,0:09:52.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:56.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Is this a park!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:07.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year! {Sigh...}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.53,0:10:12.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei and the others are already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:14.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please excuse the intrusion! {We're coming in. -Seto}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:16.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:17.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Um, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino-san! Rei-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.56,0:10:21.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, Happy New Year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:25.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sayako oba-sama, Yumi and the others have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:34.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:35.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.67,0:10:46.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-chan, you remembered, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:47.68,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm so impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.74,0:10:54.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now then. Please take care of each other this year as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please take care of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:03.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a good non-alcoholic drink, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.81,0:11:04.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:06.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're eating the ozouni already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.28,0:11:07.63,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Ozouni is a traditional type of soup often eaten with mochi at New Years. {note}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:07.65,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.95,0:11:10.72,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry from helping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.13,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:14.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It certainly does look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.41,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:17.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan made the stock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on with Touko-chan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.19,0:11:26.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That must be someone from the sushi shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.30,Marimite,,0,0,0,,They're always on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.96,0:11:32.80,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no way she'd come...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:47.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm going to start reading them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:52.85,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: The game they're playing is called "utagaruta." One person reads the first few lines of a poem, {ummmmmm}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:56.72,tlnote,,0,0,0,,and the two teams of players compete to pick out the correct name of the poem. This style of playing is specifically known as "genpei gassen". {ummmmmmmmm}{}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.49,0:11:50.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Lying all alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:55.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Through the hours of the night, till the daylight comes:"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:55.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"The Mother of Michitsuna."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're correct, Shimako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:05.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,On to the next one then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Eight-fold cherry flowers"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Eight-fold cherry flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:10.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Cherry flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.19,0:12:11.63,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,"That at Nara--ancient seat"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"Lady Ise no Osuke."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:16.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's the right one!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:17.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Shimako-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.27,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Really. She's as good as you, Sachiko. {MISSING LINE. I TLed it to this.-Seto}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.72,0:12:26.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You did better than last year, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:28.22,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get any...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:27.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.28,0:12:35.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of poems about what people brooded over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:36.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Like their troubles.{}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:39.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Aren't there one hundred different troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.99,0:12:41.62,tlnote,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)}TL Note: The game takes its poems from the Ogura Hyakunin Isshu, a collection of 100 poems by 100 different poets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.26,0:12:40.77,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But if that's how it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,people who can grab so many cards will mix up human emotions,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:49.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,and become confused, won't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:51.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.01,0:12:53.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next is Human Snakes and Ladders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.50,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Human Snakes and Ladders?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's play this by competing as pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How about grouping up according to the colors of the roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:04.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:08.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Instead of using pieces, you yourselves will be moving around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Each room in the house has a different name,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so please follow the directions in each room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.32,0:13:13.71,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:15.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.45,0:13:16.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:18.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:20.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Three is the Water Flea Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Water Flea Room?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:26.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Sachiko-san has an advantage when it comes to the rooms on the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:26.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:29.37,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You even thought that far ahead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:31.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:33.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:37.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Five is the Hippopotamus Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.26,0:13:38.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:39.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:41.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.64,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You two are going to Furisode Fish Room. Have fun. {TL Note: Furisode is a type of kimono.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.64,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Furisode is a type of kimono.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The Messy Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:50.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This isn't the right place either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.05,0:13:53.90,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Where's the room!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.92,0:13:56.26,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The Ostrich Room...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:14:00.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The number of squares on the board and the distance between rooms have no relationship, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:04.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There it is, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:06.83,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The Kimono Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.24,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi, take off your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:27.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,No matter how you think about it, the rule here is to put on one of the kimonos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.97,Marimite,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no time to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:31.60,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But I don't have to be the one to change!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.60,0:14:32.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:36.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's the younger sister's job to do these kinds of things, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:42.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Plus, it's not interesting if I change, since it'll only be a difference in color!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.92,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, accept it and strip!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.92,0:14:48.02,Marimite,,0,0,0,,W-W-W... Wait, Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.02,0:14:50.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Close the door at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:54.17,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's only women in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.67,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:01.43,tlnote,,0,0,0,,Sign: Make the younger sister wear a kimono
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-chan, you're cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:09.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Really, it suits you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.03,0:15:10.03,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.40,0:15:14.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,All teams cleared their first tasks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.69,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:23.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though I continued to experience the constricting feeling of the kimono's sash,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:26.06,Marimite,,0,0,0,,the two of us managed to complete all of the tasks given to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:29.79,Marimite,,0,0,0,,We, the Rosa Chinensis team, won.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.29,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.87,0:15:36.57,Marimite Alt,,0,0,0,,Jeez! Even though we tried so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.98,0:15:37.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Aren't you glad you came?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:41.55,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes. Although, you didn't know if anyone had anything else planned today or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:44.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you still managed to gather everyone together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.47,0:15:46.59,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This was to cheer me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You really do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:49.56,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:54.05,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I also understand that you're the one who created this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'll hold what you've done for me close to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:02.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How silly. You don't have to say that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:03.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm a friend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:11.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, Saeko obaa-sama says she'll make some matcha later! {TL Note: Matcha is the traditional type of tea made and drank in tea ceremonies.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:11.33,tlnote,,0,0,0,,TL Note: Matcha is the traditional type of tea made and drank in tea ceremonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Hurry and help us clean up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:19.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Give me the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.04,Marimite,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.87,0:16:27.84,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:30.81,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I feel so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:35.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:41.46,Marimite,,0,0,0,,For some reason, I feel like a cold wind is creeping into my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's probably because your emotions are locked in a different room in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.38,0:16:49.45,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Did I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.45,0:16:50.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:55.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Something like you were happy, but a cold wind is flowing into your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.62,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.62,0:17:01.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though two of you are here, I'm mumbling strange things to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.34,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:06.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even if the rooms with your feelings for your Onee-sama or friends are full,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:08.18,Marimite,,0,0,0,,if any of the other rooms in your heart is empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:10.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,you feel like you're missing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.86,0:17:12.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Another room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.86,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Your younger sister's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There's no such room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:16.85,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:21.28,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But you recently added the extra room for Touko's sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:27.08,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Even though you already made a room for her, there's no sister to live in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,so you have a hole in your heart right now, Yumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.62,0:17:34.95,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.44,0:17:39.48,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's what's wrong. Don't worry too much about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.76,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You said it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.38,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Shimako-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.58,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm speaking from past experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.14,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm also in the process of adding an extra room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:52.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:58.66,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A person's heart is like a house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.70,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I think of it that way, it's easy to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:07.07,Marimite,,0,0,0,,And the room shared by Onee-sama and I is already overloading.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:12.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Okay! Just as I thought, we really should write before going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:13.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Write what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:14.87,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Nakakiyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.22,0:18:19.89,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Let's sleep after we write palindromes starting with "nakakiyo" and put them under our pillows.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:22.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It's a charm for having a good first dream of the new year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:24.63,Marimite,,0,0,0,,You remembered well, Yumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:36.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm going to turn off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:38.27,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,What a sweet expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:19:01.20,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I can feel this much just from looking at my friend's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:06.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If this was my own sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:20.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,My first dream of the new year was about her. Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.29,0:19:33.15,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan was there, near my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:38.42,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But between us was a pane of clouded glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:41.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see Touko-chan's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.00,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please, Touko-chan! Wipe the glass from your side too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If you don't, the glass won't clear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.43,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.25,Marimite,,0,0,0,,There must be some kind of mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:04.16,Marimite,,0,0,0,,How can I make her understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.62,0:20:08.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.48,0:20:29.78,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.01,0:20:39.19,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:41.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:43.12,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Have a good day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:45.91,Marimite,,0,0,0,,A good day to you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.83,0:20:57.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to see Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.11,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to make her my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.33,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I want to know everything about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:10.75,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should go to Kashiwagi-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:20.01,Marimite,,0,0,0,,If I ask Kashiwagi-san, I might be able to learn more about Touko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.46,0:21:22.47,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:25.98,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan might not be happy about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.46,0:21:29.22,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Instead, she might close her heart to me. {Ky check this. It wasnt right-Seto}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:33.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:35.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That's not something an older sister would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.99,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm not qualified to be an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.86,0:21:55.10,Marimite,,0,0,0,,The third semester started before I could do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.35,0:22:03.49,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.27,0:22:15.23,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I'm pleased to see you, Yumi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:17.57,Marimite,,0,0,0,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.45,0:22:21.39,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Touko-chan was smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.03,0:22:25.74,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As if nothing happened between us last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.94,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As if there was nothing between us at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:31.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,As if she had forgotten everything on purpose.
