Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:51.20,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Somehow, despite the colors of the city, the lonely winter scenery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.20,0:22:58.89,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}makes me think of when you showed your back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:07.63,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Between the two of us is a transparent wall
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.63,0:23:17.14,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}which is turning foggy with my crystallized sighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:27.42,englished - Copy,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Window glass, window glass, so obscure that I cannot see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.61,0:23:33.66,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}even though I know that you're right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:43.63,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,100)}Whether you're laughing, or crying, show me your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.63,0:23:52.35,englished,,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,150)}Look at the glass from your side too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.76,0:24:08.09,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Rei-chan, you can't tell anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.21,Marimite,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:13.73,Marimite,,0,0,0,,When I was learning to ride a bike, that's what Rei-chan said to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.85,0:24:16.35,Marimite,,0,0,0,,But in a moment with extraordinarily bad timing, things got out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.93,0:24:18.36,Marimite,,0,0,0,,That was winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.36,0:24:21.88,Marimite,,0,0,0,,It was after Nana and Rei-chan had their competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.88,0:24:23.96,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yoshino, you cheered for Rei-chan, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.08,0:24:26.93,Marimite,,0,0,0,,"That's all right" was what Rei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.15,0:24:29.32,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Next time: The Masked Actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.75,0:24:33.53,Marimite,,0,0,0,,Yumi-san, you're experiencing painful feelings different from mine, aren't you?
